1.0.2.name: wordpress/goodbarber
1.0.2.description: GoodBarber plugin is a fork of JSON API created by dphiffer. GoodBarber plugin creates a communication interface between your WordPress and your GoodBarber account. It is used to retrieve content from your WordPress so that you can sync it with your native app created with GoodBarber.
